author: Caitlin Oprysko
title: Hogan orders Marylanders to shelter in place
description: The governor told reporters Monday that Maryland is up to 1,413 confirmed cases of the novel coronavirus.
content:
The governor told reporters Monday that Maryland is up to 1,413 confirmed cases of the novel coronavirus and that state has seen infections in individuals as young as one month old. Deaths in the state tripled over the weekend from five to 15, he said.
